4745235611,-1.31054409514602 -48.4694682221432,-1.31047477954892 -48.4694682221432,-1.31041386584238 -48.4694976287601,-1.31032144504624 -48.4695753462478,-1.31030674173777 -48.4696677670439,-1.31033824882736 -48.469819001074,-1.31036765544431 -48.4699261251786,-1.31030254079249 -48.4699576322682,-1.31023742614066 -48.4699912398304,-1.31018491432468 -48.4700542540096,-1.31011349825494 -48.4700857610992,-1.3100000727324</coordinates></LinearRing></outerBoundaryIs></Polygon>
