6366804927,-1.36179799936205 -48.436219578459,-1.36199718811276 -48.4361762765567,-1.36208032776523 -48.4361373048446,-1.36213748627631 -48.4363044501876,-1.36228211463008 -48.4363953841825,-1.36235832597818 -48.4365192276232,-1.36244319770675 -48.4365447757456,-1.3624609514867</coordinates></LinearRing></outerBoundaryIs></Polygon>
